Company Overview of Contrarius Investment Management Limited



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Contrarius Investment Management Limited is an employee owned investment manager. The firm provides its services to individuals and legal entities. It manages client focused portfolios. The firm launches equity mutual funds for its clients. It invests in public equity markets across the globe. The firm also invests in REITs. It conducts in-house fundamental research to make its investments. Contrarius Investment Management Limited was founded on April 29, 2008 and is based in St. Helier, Channel Islands.


No 2 The ForumGrenville StreetSt Helier,  JE1 4HHChannel IslandsFounded in 2008



Phone: 44 1534 828 990

Fax: 44 1534 823 001

www.contrarius.com







