On Tuesday, September 30, 2008,  a U.S. federal trademark registration was filed for 
                        CONTRARIUS by 
                        Contrarius Investment Management Limited, .
                        The USPTO has given the CONTRARIUS 
                        trademark serial  number of  79061623.  
                        The current federal status of this trademark filing is ABANDONED - EXPRESS.
                        The correspondent listed for CONTRARIUS is 
                        
                        
                                            Kevin J. Collette of 
                                            1201 3RD AVE STE 3400,  SEATTLE, WA 98101-3268,  
                                .
                            The CONTRARIUS trademark is filed in the category of 
                            
                                    Insurance & Financial Services
                                . 
                            The description provided to the USPTO for CONTRARIUS 
                            is Financial affairs, namely, fund management; financial consultation; fund investment consultation; investment of funds for others services; management of fund services, wealth management, namely, management of wealth within segregated or pooled investment vehicles; investment analysis; stock market analysis; private and institutional asset management for others, namely, fund services which offers investment opportunities; financial consultation and investment advice for private clients and institutions; provision of advice, information and consultation in relation to all the foregoing. 
                            





