        in your computer's memory (do not allow your browser to remember your Password). Consequently, we advise
        entering your Username and Password each time you begin a new browser session. Questions regarding the
        Contrarius privacy policy should be directed to the Administrator.
    

        The Privacy Policy statements only relate to the website
        www.contrarius.com
        and do not extend to any linked external websites.
    

