        The information contained on our website and email services is being made available for the benefit of the present investors in the Contrarius ICAV and its sub-funds, the Contrarius
        Global Equity Fund and the Contrarius Global Absolute Fund (collectively referred to as “the Funds”) and such other persons expressly authorised by the Funds to receive such information, 
        provided that such investors and other persons are not prohibited under the applicable laws of their citizenship, domicile or residence from receiving such information. No other 
        persons are authorised by the Funds to receive such information.
    

