Privacy Policy



        Contrarius subscribes to internationally recognised standards of personal privacy protection,
        complying with the requirement of the Data Protection (Jersey) Law 2005. Please refer to
        www.dataprotection.gov.je
        for further details and guidance.
    

        Contrarius will treat as confidential information it holds in relation to a user where that
        information is not in the public domain. Subject to this clause Contrarius will not disclose
        such confidential information to third-parties.
    

        In order to provide its services to users, Contrarius shall process any personal data it holds
        in accordance with applicable data protection legislation and may use agents and other third-parties
        in Jersey and elsewhere to hold or process personal data or other confidential information. As a
        user and party to these terms you provide your express consent to the transfer, holding and
        processing of such personal data and other confidential information in this way.
    

        Contrarius will disclose otherwise confidential personal data and confidential information if it is
        compelled to do so by laws and regulations applicable to it and/or its agents, and whether in Jersey
        or elsewhere.
    

        At any time you may change your personal information that is in the possession of Contrarius by
        contacting the Administrator.
    

        Contrarius does not sell, rent, loan, trade or lease any personal information collected, including
        application forms, financial data or email addresses.
    

        For security reasons, we do not recommend saving your Username and Password of your online user profile
        in your computer's memory (do not allow your browser to remember your Password). Consequently, we advise
        entering your Username and Password each time you begin a new browser session. Questions regarding the
        Contrarius privacy policy should be directed to the Administrator.
    

        The Privacy Policy statements only relate to the website
        www.contrarius.com
        and do not extend to any linked external websites.
    

